model.name: Polar Flat Ankle Boot
model.disambiguatingDescription: The Polar flat ankle boot comes in rubber-effect calf leather. The thick rubber outsole and rounded toe are color-matched to the upper for a distinctive "dipped-in-paint" look. Both waterproof and lightweight, this boot is easy to slip on and off thanks to its elastic side panels.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• White
  • Calf leather
  • Elastic side panels
  • Rubber outsole
  • Vuitton rubber tag
  • Patent Monogram-canvas back loop
  • Made in Italy
